&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;The Conference Producer is responsible for the end-to-end delivery of conferences, acting as the lead owner of content, product development, and industry relationships. This role oversees the full programme lifecycle, ensuring commercially viable, high-quality events that deliver value to stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
