nts and trends in the industry.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Provide market intelligence, competitor analysis and client feedback to inform overall show strategy and positioning&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Open to taking on leadership and support of leadership roles on occasion&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Open to mentoring others, including day-to-day guidance and coaching Sales Executives&lt;/p&gt;
